flowchart TD
    PipelineReady[CD pipeline ready to deploy] --> CreateRequest[Create approval request with deployment summary]
    CreateRequest --> NotifyApprovers[Notify approver group]
    NotifyApprovers --> ApproverReview[Approver reviews changelog and test results]
    ApproverReview --> Decision{Approver decision}
    Decision -->|Clarification needed| RequestInfo[Request more information]
    RequestInfo --> ApproverReview
    Decision -->|Rejected| RejectDeploy[Cancel deployment pipeline]
    RejectDeploy --> NotifyTeam[Notify team with rejection reason]
    Decision -->|Approved| TimeWindow{Within permitted deploy window?}
    TimeWindow -->|No| QueueDeploy[Queue deployment for next window]
    QueueDeploy --> TimeWindow
    TimeWindow -->|Yes| ProceedDeploy[Resume deployment pipeline]
    ProceedDeploy --> AuditLog[Record approval in audit log]
    AuditLog --> Done[Deployment proceeds to environment]
